---
// Static Faraid Guide - renders as pure HTML, no JavaScript needed
---

<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-warm-200 p-6 md:p-10 space-y-10">

  <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center p-3 bg-teal-100 rounded-full mb-4">
      <!-- BookOpen icon (inline SVG) -->
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-6 h-6 text-teal-700"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-warm-800 mb-4 font-display">Memahami Faraid di Malaysia</h2>
    <p class="text-warm-600 leading-relaxed">
      Faraid adalah undang-undang pewarisan Islam. Di Malaysia, ia adalah kaedah lalai (default) untuk pembahagian harta pusaka orang Islam kecuali semua waris bersetuju dengan kaedah lain (Takharuj).
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

    <!-- Section 1 -->
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h3 class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold text-teal-800 font-display">
        <!-- CheckCircle2 icon -->
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
        Perkara Wajib Sebelum Faraid
      </h3>
      <p class="text-warm-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        Sebelum harta dibahagikan mengikut Faraid, perkara berikut mesti diselesaikan daripada harta kasar:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-3">
        <li class="flex gap-3 text-sm text-warm-700 bg-warm-50 p-3 rounded-lg border border-warm-200">
          <span class="font-bold text-teal-600">1.</span>
          <span><strong>Kos Pengurusan Jenazah:</strong> Kos yang munasabah untuk memandi, mengafan, dan mengebumikan jenazah.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3 text-sm text-warm-700 bg-warm-50 p-3 rounded-lg border border-warm-200">
          <span class="font-bold text-teal-600">2.</span>
          <span><strong>Hutang:</strong> Hutang kepada Allah (Zakat, Fidyah, Kaffarah) dan hutang sesama manusia.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3 text-sm text-warm-700 bg-warm-50 p-3 rounded-lg border border-warm-200">
          <span class="font-bold text-teal-600">3.</span>
          <span><strong>Harta Sepencarian:</strong> Harta yang dituntut oleh pasangan yang masih hidup (biasanya sebahagian daripada harta perolehan bersama) di Mahkamah Syariah.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3 text-sm text-warm-700 bg-warm-50 p-3 rounded-lg border border-warm-200">
          <span class="font-bold text-teal-600">4.</span>
          <span><strong>Wasiat:</strong> Maksimum 1/3 daripada baki harta untuk bukan waris atau tujuan amal jariah.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 2 -->
    <div class="space-y-4">
       <h3 class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xl font-bold text-teal-800 font-display">
        <!-- HelpCircle icon -->
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
        Waris Utama (Ashab al-Furud)
      </h3>
      <p class="text-warm-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        Waris utama yang tidak akan terhalang daripada mewarisi harta (kecuali terdapat halangan seperti pembunuhan atau berlainan agama).
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="bg-teal-50/50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-teal-100">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-teal-900 text-sm">Pasangan (Suami/Isteri)</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-warm-600 mt-1">Suami mendapat 1/2 (tiada anak) atau 1/4 (ada anak). Isteri mendapat 1/4 (tiada anak) atau 1/8 (ada anak).</p>
        </div>
         <div class="bg-teal-50/50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-teal-100">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-teal-900 text-sm">Ibu Bapa</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-warm-600 mt-1">Bapa dan Ibu masing-masing mendapat 1/6 jika si mati mempunyai anak.</p>
        </div>
         <div class="bg-teal-50/50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-teal-100">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-teal-900 text-sm">Anak-anak</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-warm-600 mt-1">Anak lelaki dan perempuan mengambil baki (Asabah). Anak lelaki menerima dua kali ganda bahagian anak perempuan (Nisbah 2:1).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-amber-50 rounded-xl border border-amber-200">
    <h4 class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-amber-800 mb-2">
        <!-- AlertCircle icon -->
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
        Penafian (Disclaimer)
    </h4>
    <p class="text-sm text-amber-800/80 leading-relaxed">
        Kalkulator ini adalah untuk tujuan pendidikan dan memberikan anggaran berdasarkan Mazhab Syafi'i yang diamalkan di Malaysia. Kes-kes rumit yang melibatkan datuk, saudara-mara (Kalalah), atau isteri berbilang hendaklah dirujuk kepada Peguam Syarie bertauliah atau unit pusaka di institusi seperti Amanah Raya atau Baitulmal.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
    <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-700 to-teal-800 hover:from-teal-800 hover:to-teal-900 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl transition no-underline">
      <!-- Calculator icon -->
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><rect x="4" y="2" width="16" height="20" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="6" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="16" y1="14" x2="16" y2="18"/><line x1="8" y1="10" x2="8" y2="10.01"/><line x1="12" y1="10" x2="12" y2="10.01"/><line x1="16" y1="10" x2="16" y2="10.01"/><line x1="8" y1="14" x2="8" y2="14.01"/><line x1="12" y1="14" x2="12" y2="14.01"/><line x1="8" y1="18" x2="8" y2="18.01"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12" y2="18.01"/></svg>
      Cuba Kalkulator Faraid
    </a>
    <a href="/hubungi" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white hover:bg-warm-50 text-warm-700 font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl border border-warm-200 transition no-underline">
      <!-- MessageCircle icon -->
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5"><path d="m3 21 1.9-5.7a8.5 8.5 0 1 1 3.8 3.8z"/></svg>
      Hubungi Kami
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Panduan Lanjut -->
  <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-warm-200">
    <p class="text-center text-xs font-medium text-warm-400 mb-3">Panduan Lanjut</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-sm">
      <a href="/apa-itu-faraid" class="text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700 hover:underline transition">Apa Itu Faraid?</a>
      <a href="/jadual-pembahagian-faraid" class="text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700 hover:underline transition">Jadual Pembahagian</a>
      <a href="/harta-sepencarian" class="text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700 hover:underline transition">Harta Sepencarian</a>
      <a href="/faraid-suami-meninggal" class="text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700 hover:underline transition">Faraid Suami Meninggal</a>
      <a href="/pembahagian-harta-mengikut-faraid" class="text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700 hover:underline transition">Pembahagian Harta</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
